es/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89719cd1d9f7983cc0d701d8036cc21bd16180dc","tid":1823454,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29c750b6c2e9843494870c6c2f630038676017d1","tid":1823454,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b34e0cddad93f20c26bbe209a28d7a3c11893d1d","tid":1823454,"uid":95499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T16:45:54.000Z","msg":"咁唔比較咪得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:16:47.000Z","msg":"好難，同埋平時都有說話聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef9ca2992434996f4d4da07a9e2b34a7ad00fd5","tid":1823454,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa68025ff90ba4b1e8fc8224ed7ff109346bfd0c","tid":1823454,"uid":271968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T17:05:30.000Z","msg":"我明呀 成日迫自己唔好同人比<br />\n但一睇到有關佢地嘅嘢<br />\n就自己心裡暗暗地同人比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但要果啲係自己好朋友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T06:17:42.000Z","msg":"其實都正常<br />\n佢地暗地裡都應該會同你比較"},{"pid":"19ffc956dc1cf9786a6a6d491545395b1e088c1c","tid":1823454,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af0a839649c8123b31240bd506d4dc8bd7d50b2c","tid":1823454,"uid":141237,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T17:25:44.000Z","msg":"所以我從20歲開始就開始做gym，<br />\n透過做gym每日提醒自己，<br />\n<br />\n你一停，響你後面既人就會超越你，你之前所有做過既嘢都會白費，你只能夠不斷前進，其他人先超越唔到你，相反，而你將不斷超越果d本身響你前面而中途放棄左既人。<br />\n<br />\n只要你肯不斷push自己，增值自己，無論由外到內，知識、技巧、外型、氣場都不斷提升個quality，到時你再睇返以前同你同level既人，果d由始至終都無努力過既人，你就會知道自己既價值係咩。<br />\n<br />\n唔好講咩咁做人好辛苦，人生本身就係不斷學習，不斷探索自己，只有不斷提升自己，先可以搵到真正既自己，先可以真正了解自己。<br 